{"tid":156724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰：林鄭不獲主流民意支持 不應參選特首","createTime":"2017-03-15T02:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T14:17:14.000Z","uid":22609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f81866dac08da9363657d071f1ec2e2ce796bb5","tid":156724,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1979Vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1979Vx.jpg&h=9f7b2094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正在北京出席兩會的田北辰說昨日辯論，他對林鄭昨日在特首選舉論壇的表現「跌眼鏡」，「政治議題是香港今日撕裂的原因，我們需要一個好政治敏感的特首，香港要啲嘢中央唔想的話，你點同香港人解釋，你點同中央解釋，呢個最難搞。」<br />\n<br />\n對於林鄭稱如果不獲主流民意支持，她會辭任行政長官，田北辰稱自己「跌晒眼鏡」，「佢有無諗過民調，佢今日係負淨值（即不支持率高於支持率），曾俊華係正，曾俊華只有單位數字反對，她有40幾%，你睇主流民意根本不應該參選。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/批林鄭-辭職論-田北辰-很難說服自己支持她-暫傾向支持曾俊華/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%89%B9%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E8%AB%96-%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0-%E5%BE%88%E9%9B%A3%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A5%B9-%E6%9A%AB%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%2F&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9c95d373\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%89%B9%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E8%AB%96-%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0-%E5%BE%88%E9%9B%A3%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A5%B9-%E6%9A%AB%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%2F&h=e11f8ed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/批林鄭-辭職論-田北辰-很難說服自己支持她-暫傾向支持曾俊華/</a>"},{"pid":"d6b726463a827d0d552a40884b0b6ec9ccc0d02f","tid":156724,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"288eee5472a0b0bccb407f3edfa562b128a22bf1","tid":156724,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:39:15